originalText.text:
Dr. Mickey is what they call him. He is one doctor that will give you medication for the pain there's no mistake. But he is also a doctor that will make you piss test every time for that same prescription.

I would not recommend going to for injections. Due to my story.

Dr Mickey gave me three injections. The first injection was right where I asked for it to be. The second injection he told me it doesn't matter and he can't answer my question on why he wants to put it on the side that doesn't hurt.

It's not until after I complain of more new pain on the side that doesn't hurt at all. He wants to go ahead and give me a third injection in the spot where the pain actually was. Please do not deal with this doctor if you don't want any new pain. Only go to him if you want medication and be prepared to take a piss test.

originalText.text: I love Dr Fukshansky because of him I’ll stay here at this office. He really cares about the patients and he take time to ask about your past and what helped and how he can make it better. He don’t look old but he has old school doctor ways and that’s what I was looking for! He will always been my doctor his wisdom is amazing I have a complicated medical condition and he is the first doctor I didn’t have to explain it to he knew about it

originalText.text: Dr. Fukshansky is incredible. He is patient, knowledgeable, and compassionate. One of the best doctors I have ever gone to AND I am 72. If you are in pain go see him. You won’t be sorry!!!
